textAfterTable: 12 Songs Album Review American death metal masters Cannibal Corpse make a gory return with their eleventh album, Torture. Working once again with producer Erik Rutan (who also plays guitar in Hate Eternal), the band continues to push its sound to brutal new limits, and with songs like "As Deep as the Knife Will Go" and "Demented Aggression," it's clear that the gore-obsessed band shows no signs of slowing down., Rovi Customer Reviews love it           by fuzzy104 everytime i hear cannibal corpse i always think of ace ventura!!
